article.description: — CJ Fleming scored 23 points, Dylan Penn added 20 points and six rebounds, and Bellarmine beat Florida Gulf Coast 74-63 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Fleming, Penn lead Bellarmine past Florida Gulf Coast 74-63
article.linkText: Fleming, Penn lead Bellarmine past Florida Gulf Coast 74-63
article.story: FORT MYERS, Fla. -- — CJ Fleming scored 23 points, Dylan Penn added 20 points and six rebounds, and Bellarmine beat Florida Gulf Coast 74-63 on Saturday night. Ethan Claycomb had 13 points for Bellarmine (13-9, 7-1 Atlantic Sun Conference). Alec Pfriem added 11 points. Juston Betz had a career-high 10 assists plus nine rebounds. Tavian Dunn-Martin had 24 points for Florida Gulf Coast (13-9, 3-5). Kevin Samuel added 10 points, 10 rebounds and four assists. Cyrus Largie had seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
